[I] OpenGL image compositing library

[T] Glitz is an OpenGL image compositing library. Glitz provides Porter/Duff
[T] compositing of images and implicit mask generation for geometric primitives
[T] including trapezoids, triangles, and rectangles.
[T]
[T] The semantics of glitz are designed to precisely match the specification
[T] of the X Render extension.

[U] https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/glitz/

